race.comment: Former NSW galloper AGED CARE (6) just ran into one better when having the first run for the new stable before getting the job done here at the latest effort. Should sit up on speed and looks the runner in this field that they all have to run down. NORTHERNONTAP (3) loves it here around this Townsville circuit with three wins and three seconds from nine outings. Has to be included in calculations. HIGHBAR (2) was too bad to be true last time out but the form prior was up to this. Can bounce right back without surprising. WINNING SAGA (5) resumes but has tuned up for this with a recent trial and is a three-time winner at this track. Can run a race while fresh. INDEFINITE (8) rounds out the selections with the claim.
